directions: Stir beans, chicken, Alfredo sauce, chicken broth, green chilies, yellow corn, white corn, Monterey Jack cheese, pepperjack cheese, sour cream, cumin, garlic, white pepper, and cayenne pepper together in a slow cooker.
Cook on Low, stirring occasionally, 3 to 4 hours.
ingredients: 3 (15 ounce) cans great Northern beans, rinsed and drained
title: Cheesy Slow Cooker White Chili
